MICROVIEW TECHNO said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 71.55% to NT$79,388,000 from NT$279,042,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales             79,388          279,042    
YOY%             -71.55%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            284,107          882,404    
YOY%             -67.80% 
=================================================================
 